Introduction

This file contains the instructions to run a the script called run_analysis.R. 

This script contains several task as:

Read some data from ./data/UCI HAR Dataset/ repository 
(The content can be download at https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip )
Do some transformations
Export the tiny data to a txt file in ~ repository.
The codebook_run_analysis.md contains the structure of this file.

Run from command line

Clone this repo
Run the script:

$ Rscript run_analysis.R

Look for the final dataset at AverageMeanStd.txt

